### 1. GET ALL TASKS (Should be empty list [] initially)
GET http://localhost:8080/tasks

### 2. CREATE A NEW TASK (Send an order to the kitchen)
POST http://localhost:8080/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Study for Exam",
  "description": "Complete Unit 1 and Unit 2 revision",
  "isCompleted": false
}

### 3. GET ALL TASKS AGAIN (Should show the task you just created)
GET http://localhost:8080/tasks

### 4. UPDATE THE TASK (Mark as completed)
PUT http://localhost:8080/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Study for Exam",
  "description": "Unit 1 and 2 DONE",
  "isCompleted": true
}

### 5. DELETE THE TASK
DELETE http://localhost:8080/tasks/1